Parliament, Tuesday 12 March 2019 – The Select Committee on Education and Recreation, will tomorrow be briefed by the Department of Higher Education and Training on registration at Universities and TVET Colleges. Details of the meeting are as follows: Date: 13 March 2019
	Venue: Committee Room M201, Second Floor, Marks Building,
	Time: 10:00 ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE SELECT COMMITTEE ON EDUCATION AND RECREATION, MS LUNGELWA ZWANE. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Mava Lukani (Mr)
